<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
</head>
<body>
<p>
  Hi <%= @account.first_name %>, <br>
</p>

<p>
  We have received a password reset request for your Xcelyst account. To proceed with resetting your password, please use the following One-Time Password (OTP):
</p>
<p>
  OTP: <%= @account.otp %>
  Expiration: 5 minutes
</p>

<p>
  If you did not initiate this password reset request, we strongly advise you to take immediate action to secure your account by changing your password.
</p>

<p>
  Thank you for trusting Xcelyst with your account. If you have any questions or need further assistance, please don't hesitate to contact our support team at info@xcelyst.com.
</p>
<%= render 'layouts/email_footer'%>
</body>
</html>
